{"tid":1146658,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟4】刪減場面合集！Robert Downey Jr.自爆有另一個英雄死亡結局","createTime":"2019-05-09T11:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T15:53:47.000Z","uid":66923,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f83e784358630f60f477783a009d2a8214f813","tid":1146658,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"《復仇者聯盟4︰終局之戰》（Avengers: Endgame）劇透禁令在羅素兄弟的宣布下，已經逐漸解除，身為主演的鐵甲奇俠（Iron Man／Tony Stark）（Robert Downey Jr.飾）在個人IG旋即公開了一條劇透短片，影片中驚見《復4》 原來有另一個結局，此外羅素兄弟亦向外媒透露了不少在電影中刪減的場面。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.Marvel三大巨頭死兩個</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nRobert Downey Jr.日前在IG上公開了一條於片場拍攝的片段，從畫面上可以見到披著紅斗蓬躺臥在地上，而美國隊長則被魁隆掐頸並舉高，最後美國隊長無力地垂下掙扎的雙手，而身亡告終，最後只有鐵甲奇俠存活。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BxJEjXPAsAa/?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBxJEjXPAsAa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_button_share_sheet&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYef4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=b83e930b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBxJEjXPAsAa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_button_share_sheet&h=3a25667d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BxJEjXPAsAa/?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTY1znS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTY1znS.jpg&h=08384ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國隊長被掐頸令人回想起這一幕<br />\n<br />\n不知道大家記不記得變形俠醫（麥克雷法路／Mark Alan Ruffalo飾）曾對外媒說羅素兄弟為防止劇透總共拍下了5個結局，相信這次Robert Downey Jr.公開的就是其中一個。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hci1zn0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHci1zn0.jpg&h=387f35d0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KKoNH0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KKoNH0.jpg&h=c2a60478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2.雷神和女武神親吻</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkej5vb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxkej5vb.jpg&h=f895fd17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家還記得電影中戰爭後，雷神和女武神在一段對話後，就各奔東西的畫面嗎？羅素兄弟日前於外國電影SiriusXM中表示其實雷神和女武神當時有一場親吻畫面：當女武神把手放在雷神的膊頭時，雷神順勢給了她一個吻，而女武神隨即問他：「你在做甚麼？（WhatWhat are you doing?!）」，接著雷神說：「我以為⋯⋯剛才那個觸碰是⋯⋯（Oh, I thought that touch..）」，女武神解釋道：「不！那只是一個告別式觸碰（No, that was, like, a goodbye touch）」（影片由15:37開始)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=dwjLg1lLPGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdwjLg1lLPGk&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYef4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=aa96b48c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=dwjLg1lLPGk</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fz5Gzot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFz5Gzot.jpg&h=553c9b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅素兄弟認為這個場面非常搞笑，但因為剛完結戰爭和Iron Man的葬禮，這一刻的搞笑好像顯得不合時宜，所以不得不刪除了這個有趣互動的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3.Iron Man曾和長大後的女兒見面</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rit5gBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRit5gBA.jpg&h=42a4c070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家還記得《復仇者聯盟3︰無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）中，魁隆彈指後見到女兒嘉魔娜（Gamora）的場面嗎？羅素兄弟表示他們本來讓這集同樣彈指後的Iron Man看到長大後的女兒Morgan Stark，但考慮到電影分支太多，不想觀眾混淆，而且長大後的女兒無法引起觀眾在情感上的共嗚，因此狠心刪除了這個畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Q5SF3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Q5SF3c.jpg&h=651c83b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影上映前，一直有傳Netflix火紅劇集《漢娜的遺言》（13 Reasons Why）女主角嘉芙蓮&middot;蘭福（Katherine Langford）有份參演《復4》，而且本人亦對這次拍攝非常興奮，更為角色染了頭紅髮，可惜所拍攝的片段最後沒有曝光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtK8eoj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtK8eoj.jpg&h=344cf475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅素兄弟日前在MTV推出的知名播客「Happy Sad Confused」裏表示，嘉芙蓮蘭科原本確實預定在《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》中演出，事實上她也真的演出了，但整個片段最後卻被刪除了，讓嘉芙蓮蘭科在Marvel電影宇宙（MCU）出道的機會消失了。而她飾演的角色，正是如同魁隆在神秘空間裏看到的嘉魔娜：她是Morgan Stark，Tony Stark無緣見到的未來版女兒Morgan。"},{"pid":"b4936b5a530210fd44d51cfdfb388727a760d346","tid":1146658,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b4f2e883a5fa67687e44cbb16522ec450d5c2e","tid":1146658,"uid":14652,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"接受唔到最後果場戲刪左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c760153fe372e523fc04aff2b058aea7d615a229","tid":1146658,"uid":65686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4c5f877a71cca1374a3efbfb685f5eaf692b9e","tid":1146658,"uid":41453,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:10:05.000Z","msg":"DC咩咁多delete scenes"},{"pid":"c8c17ac977b69b52ff53768c4dcc6f42f6cb4cdd","tid":1146658,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"即係有導演版啦，之前又話無谷票房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7e8f855f3f622eea15254b13c548295164d4d2","tid":1146658,"uid":229224,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"希望Blue-Ray屌一個director true cut出嚟"},{"pid":"a237473f7c1a530096c3f8d5aac99f215a2c29d8","tid":1146658,"uid":54930,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:15:18.000Z","msg":"想睇thor咀valkyrie <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2454ca3019773167a21fcd60a383ed99ae37ce4c","tid":1146658,"uid":117200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:16:35.000Z","msg":"羅素兄弟話藍光碟會有4小時版本"},{"pid":"83594be21f7fa35c92a78cc5948991c41226bd23","tid":1146658,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike"